Before running the app we needd to run it EC2 on port 8501 as all Streamlit app are running on it, and run below command in te console 
sudo apt update
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt upgrade -y
sudo apt install git curl unzip tar make sudo vim wget -y
sudo apt install git curl unzip tar make sudo vim wget -y
git clone "Your-repository"
sudo apt install python3-pip
pip3 install -r requirements.txt
#Temporary running
python3 -m streamlit run app.py
#Permanent running
nohup python3 -m streamlit run app.py
